Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and his friends undergo intense training
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in preparation for the showdown in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:41.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen suddenly sends an \Nelite group of Arrancars before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:46.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsugaya's advance troops \Nand Ichigo confront them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but they have trouble fighting the Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:59.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Aizen's true goal was to\N take Orihime Inoue to Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:08.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime gives into Ulquiorra's threats\N and agrees to go to Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:12.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She is given twelve hours to\N tell one person goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:20.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And so Orihime goes to Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:09.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, screaming in my sleep\N and falling out of bed is so clichéd...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw... My head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's healed... Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:32.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:40.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably Orihime Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come immediately, Kurosaki... \NIt's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}RANGIKU MATSUMOTO \NORIHIME INOUE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:01.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone gathered here in Inoue's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the status of the\N Spiritual Wave interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... We've managed to regulate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Put me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake?\N This isn't the Head Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had him switch over to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because I'm the last person\N who saw Orihime Inoue{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}before she went into the Senkaimon\N in order to go over to your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:39.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Judging from your reaction,\N it doesn't seem like she's arrived there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this, Ukitake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Inoue disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you know anything?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you my assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The two guards I had placed with her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when she went through the Senkaimon came back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,According to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that Orihime Inoue
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:12.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has either been abducted\N or killed by the Arrancars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake! \NThat's jumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to say this either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was just stating the\N worst possible scenario.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,According to our information,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime Inoue was attacked by an Arrancar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:39.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and then disappeared with the Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no proof,\N but you say that she's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:56.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was seriously injured\N in yesterday's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one here could \Nheal my wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I woke up this morning,\N it had been healed without a trace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...\NHere! On my wrist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's still some of\N Inoue's Spiritual Pressure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still going to say\N that Inoue's dead now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is unfortunate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:24.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunate?\N What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:30.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is as you say,\N then Orihime Inoue is indeed alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it also means that this is an act of treachery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Treachery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:45.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she had been abducted,\N she wouldn't have had the time to meet you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:51.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, the fact that she healed \Nyour wounds and disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:58.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,means that Orihime Inoue went\N to the Arrancars of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:08.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just worsen your position\N if you talk any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're saying,\N Head Captain Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:20.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hitsugaya advance troop member\N and Squad 6 Lieutenant Renji Abarai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:26.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will head to Hueco Mundo to bring\N the traitor, Orihime Inoue, to her senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:40.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We now know that the Arrancars\N are ready for battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the members of the\N Hitsugaya advance troop{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:48.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are to return immediately\N and defend Soul Society.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:55.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\N you want us to abandon Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:04.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We cannot risk the whole world over one life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:10.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, Head Captain,\N I cannot follow that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:18.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought this may happen,\N so I'm glad that I have prepared for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:37.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how things stand...\NAll of you, head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been ordered to take you\N back by force if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:01.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't ask\N Soul Society to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:07.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but at least tell me how\N I can get into Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue is our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go save her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:16.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:33.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We need your help in this battle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:37.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't allow you to plot your own \Ncourse of action and die for nothing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stand by until you receive orders!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:09:59.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:36.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This was on the ground outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:43.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pick up things if you \Ndon't know what they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but it was right in front of our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he go through\N the trouble to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandages? Why bandages? Why, why bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}THANKS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, why, why, why, why bandages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:08.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?\N What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely dinner first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:18.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Before that,\N a passionate embrace by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Ichi-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate. I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:30.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise Yuzu won't be \Nable to clear the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:43.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... \NI don't feel like eating today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu made all of your favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's all right. \NYou don't need to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:57.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it in the refrigerator.\N Eat it when you feel hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come dad, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just apologized three times! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an amazing new Japanese record!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\N You're acting gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's that, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you constipated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's lame. That's lame, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Could you move from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh... Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind of out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Palm reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take a look at mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've seen you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:12.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sad. I didn't think \Nthat you wanted to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been hospitalized\N due to an accident, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... \N What do you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pounding on him. \N Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:20.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed your hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for noticing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed it three weeks ago, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hand looks sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It does...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, Ichigo, Ichigo, Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing \Nduring the month you took off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:56.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried about you!\N You didn't answer your cell phone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I was a little busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Mizuiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:13.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get some tickets\N for the screening of Bad Shield 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's December 5th...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:27.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mizuiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back by then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:36.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Tatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:54.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not at home or anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Her presence has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:09.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking all over the place,\N but she's not anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:18.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where Orihime went, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, did she really disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been able to sense her, \Nbut her presence has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sense her nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, I could only faintly sense her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if she was on the\N other side of some wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But yesterday, she suddenly vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so pesky!\N I told you, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I don't know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You wear a black kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:20.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you fight strange people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:22.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything you're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arisawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I your buddy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:13.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've saved you many times\N when you've cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you troubled many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've saved you many, many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:25.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't hide things from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:29.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Keigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:44.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Tatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't bother with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:01.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it was \Nabout time you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:17.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:30.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that I might know\N a way into Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:45.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid that Aizen\N would go after Inoue's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I left her out of this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:58.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking her feelings into consideration,\N it was a mistake to leave her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:04.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do anything I can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be going against\N Soul Society's judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because I went\Nagainst them in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking pretty glum, 	Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:38.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to go to Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:39.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard the details from Mr. Urahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:47.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! I appreciate your concern, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At your strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:15.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think that I'm not strong enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take this on by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what friends are for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're finally prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:25.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are terrifying Hollows waiting\N for you in Hueco Mundo! Brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Hey, why are leading us, Kon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:28.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going with us to Hueco Mundo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:30.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:33.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the important role of\N protecting the girls of this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:37.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:41.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You appeared at a really appropriate time back there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:44.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hiding with Captain Zaraki, \Nwaiting for your time to appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:45.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:47.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:48.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:51.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:51.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:53.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You did that for us, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:57.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:03.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed lots of time with Captain Zaraki.